From 43111d802dca891fc26e034f38eccd81d6a54f76 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tomaz Zaman <tomaz@mono.si>
Date: Mon, 2 Mar 2026 12:40:37 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 2/6] ncsw: port DPAA1 NCSW layer to ARM64

- New: dflags_arm64.h, xx_arm64.c, core_arm64.c, fm_ehash.c
- BMan/QMan/FMan: endianness fixes, portal init for ARM64
- types_freebsd.h, dpaa_integration_ext.h: LS1046A definitions
- MURAM batch-write pattern for ARM64 store coalescing
- Portal deferred RX via mbufq to prevent NCSW_PLOCK reentry
